summary: A no-load-screen home for Skyrim. This home is fully accessible within the exterior cell.
descriptionHtml:
Sometimes, you just need a place to rest your feet, stow your things, and relax with a few crafts.Â  This little home is designed to provide basic accommodations without all the frills and fanfare of the over-decorated and overpowered mansion style homes. It is suitable for rustic and hunter lifestyles.

WARNING: This mod was designed utilizing all expansions.
